wikipedia_page.main: Harry Edward Dearden  (born 7 May 1997) is an English cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Leicestershire on 12 September 2016 in the 2016 County Championship. He made his List A debut for Leicestershire in the 2018 Royal London One-Day Cup on 7 June 2018. He made his Twenty20 debut for Leicestershire in the 2018 t20 Blast on 17 August 2018.
